Class Move.NullMove

java.lang.Object
engine.forBoard.Move
engine.forBoard.Move.NullMove
Enclosing class:
Move
public static class Move.NullMove extends Move
The NullMove class represents a placeholder for no move in a chess game. It is used as a sentinel value to indicate the absence of a valid move.
Author:
Aaron Ho
